ins can be purchased using a payment plan.</div></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><b>FAQs</b></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><b>Can I use the logo shown next to the domain?</b></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><div>Absolutely, each domain name comes with a royalty-free logo that you can use exclusively for your own company, product, or service.\r\n\r\n</div></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><b>Are monthly installments available for all domains?</b></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><div>Sellers can choose specifically which domains to sell using <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://alter.com/buyers#installments\">monthly installments</a> so not all domains can be purchased using a payment plan.\r\n\r\n</div></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><b>Are there any other fees besides the price of the domain?</b></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><div>Nope, domain prices are all-inclusive. There are no other hidden fees or charges.\r\n\r\n</div></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><b>How can I check for trademark conflicts around a name?</b></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><div>You can use&nbsp;<b>3.wipo.int/branddb/en/&nbsp;&nbsp;</b>to perform free basic searches yourself. However, trademarks are a complicated subject so we recommend talking to a trademark attorney. For instance, you may still be able to use a name even if it\'s trademarked if your business is in a different industry.\r\n\r\n</div></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><b>What is your refund policy?</b></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><div>domain-marketplace serves as a third-party marketplace for domain names. Refunds and exchanges are not allowed once an order has been placed, except in the case that the domain seller fails to initiate the domain name transfer within 10 business days from the time of purchase. Buyers are advised to perform all necessary due diligence prior to making a purchase.\r\n\r\n</div></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><b>Where can I get additional help if I still have questions?</b></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><div><div>Get in touch with our support team <b>(support@domain-marketplace)</b>at any time.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br><b>We\'re always happy to help!</b></div></div><div><div><br></div></div></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><br></div><div><div><br></div></div><div><br></div><div></div>'],
